headline: Union Pacific Honors 16 Companies with Annual Sustainability Partner Award
summary: OMAHA, Neb., November 12, 2024--Union Pacific Railroad proudly recognized 16 customers and suppliers with the railroad’s 2024 Sustainability Partner Award. This is the second year Union Pacific awarded innovative partners who demonstrated leadership and progress toward achieving their sustainability goals.
